<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #F3F4F6; padding: 20px;">

  <div style="border: 1px solid #002130; width:100%; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="background-color: #002130; font-weight: bold; color: #E3E4E7; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem;">
      Requisition Request Rejected
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 30px; font-size: 1.2rem;">
      <p>
        Dear <%= @requisition_details[:requester_name] %>,
      </p>

      <p>
        Unfortunately, your requisition request 
      for 
        "<em><%= @requisition.purpose %></em>" has been rejected.
      </p>

      <p>
        Kindly review and revise the stated purpose to ensure it appropriately aligns with the requested amount. 
        Once updated, you may resubmit the requisition for further consideration.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank You<br/><%@requisition_details[:supervisor_full_name]%></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #6c757d;">
    <p>Informatics Team. <%= Time.current.year %></p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
